{"id": "webh_chat", "modality": "web", "name": "Chat", "task": {"description": "Build a messaging app 'Pulse' at 1920px wide: LEFT conversation list (320px) with a search box and at least 6 conversation rows (avatar, name, last-message snippet, time, and some with an unread count badge); RIGHT a chat thread with a header (contact name + avatar + online dot), a scrollable message area showing at least 8 alternating bubbles (incoming left-aligned, outgoing right-aligned, with timestamps), and a fixed composer at the bottom (text input + send button). The two panes share the same top and bottom edges. Responsive: at 375px only the chat thread shows with a back arrow; the conversation list is hidden.", "requirements": ["Two panes (conversation list and chat thread) share the same top and bottom edge", "The conversation list has a search box and at least 6 rows, each with avatar, name, snippet, and time", "At least some conversations show an unread count badge, right-aligned", "The chat thread has a header with contact name, avatar, and an online indicator", "At least 8 message bubbles appear: incoming bubbles left-aligned, outgoing bubbles right-aligned", "Each message bubble has a timestamp and does not overflow the thread width", "A composer (input + send button) is pinned to the bottom of the thread and does not overlap messages", "Incoming vs outgoing bubbles use consistent, distinct styling (repetition + contrast)", "On desktop nothing overflows horizontally", "At 375px only the chat thread is shown (with a back affordance) and the conversation list is hidden"], "difficulty": "hard"}, "runs": [{"run": 1, "ss_n_defects": 8, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 4870, "rv_n_defects": 2, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 25440}, {"run": 2, "ss_n_defects": 2, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 5184, "rv_n_defects": 2, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 23880}, {"run": 3, "ss_n_defects": 5, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 5258, "rv_n_defects": 2, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 24247}], "ss_img": "images/web/webh_chat_ss.jpg", "rv_img": "images/web/webh_chat_rv.jpg", "ss_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Pulse - Messaging App</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;\n            background: #f8f9fa;\n            height: 100vh;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .app-container {\n            display: flex;\n            height: 100vh;\n            max-width: 1920px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            background: white;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        /* LEFT PANEL - Conversation List */\n        .conversation-panel {\n            width: 320px;\n            background: #ffffff;\n            border-right: 1px solid #e9ecef;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n        }\n\n        .conversation-header {\n            padding: 24px 20px;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;\n            background: #6366f1;\n            color: white;\n        }\n\n        .app-title {\n            font-size: 28px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            margin-bottom: 16px;\n        }\n\n        .search-box {\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        .search-input {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 12px 16px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 24px;\n            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);\n            color: white;\n            font-size: 14px;\n            outline: none;\n        }\n\n        .search-input::placeholder {\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);\n        }\n\n        .conversation-list {\n            flex: 1;\n            overflow-y: auto;\n        }\n\n        .conversation-item {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            padding: 16px 20px;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f3f4;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.2s;\n        }\n\n        .conversation-item:hover {\n            background: #f8f9fa;\n        }\n\n        .conversation-item.active {\n            background: #e0e7ff;\n            border-right: 3px solid #6366f1;\n        }\n\n        .avatar {\n            width: 48px;\n            height: 48px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #8b5cf6);\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            color: white;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            font-size: 18px;\n            margin-right: 12px;\n            flex-shrink: 0;\n        }\n\n        .conversation-content {\n            flex: 1;\n            min-width: 0;\n        }\n\n        .conversation-top {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            align-items: center;\n            margin-bottom: 4px;\n        }\n\n        .contact-name {\n            font-weight: 600;\n            font-size: 16px;\n            color: #1f2937;\n        }\n\n        .conversation-time {\n            font-size: 12px;\n            color: #6b7280;\n        }\n\n        .last-message {\n            font-size: 14px;\n            color: #6b7280;\n            white-space: nowrap;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            text-overflow: ellipsis;\n            margin-right: 8px;\n        }\n\n        .conversation-bottom {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n\n        .unread-badge {\n            background: #ef4444;\n            color: white;\n            border-radius: 12px;\n            padding: 2px 8px;\n            font-size: 12px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            min-width: 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        /* RIGHT PANEL - Chat Thread */\n        .chat-panel {\n            flex: 1;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            background: #ffffff;\n        }\n\n        .chat-header {\n            padding: 20px 24px;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            background: white;\n        }\n\n        .back-button {\n            display: none;\n            background: none;\n            border: none;\n            font-size: 20px;\n            color: #6366f1;\n            margin-right: 16px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            padding: 8px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n        }\n\n        .back-button:hover {\n            background: #f3f4f6;\n        }\n\n        .chat-contact-info {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            flex: 1;\n        }\n\n        .chat-avatar {\n            width: 40px;\n            height: 40px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981, #059669);\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            color: white;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            margin-right: 12px;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        .online-dot {\n            position: absolute;\n            bottom: 2px;\n            right: 2px;\n            width: 12px;\n            height: 12px;\n            background: #10b981;\n            border: 2px solid white;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n        }\n\n        .chat-contact-name {\n            font-size: 18px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            color: #1f2937;\n        }\n\n        .chat-messages {\n            flex: 1;\n            overflow-y: auto;\n            padding: 24px;\n            background: #f8f9fa;\n        }\n\n        .message {\n            display: flex;\n            margin-bottom: 16px;\n            align-items: flex-end;\n        }\n\n        .message.incoming {\n            justify-content: flex-start;\n        }\n\n        .message.outgoing {\n            justify-content: flex-end;\n        }\n\n        .message-bubble {\n            max-width: 60%;\n            padding: 12px 16px;\n            border-radius: 18px;\n            font-size: 14px;\n            line-height: 1.4;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        .message.incoming .message-bubble {\n            background: white;\n            color: #1f2937;\n            border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\n            box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        .message.outgoing .message-bubble {\n            background: #6366f1;\n            color: white;\n            border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\n        }\n\n        .message-time {\n            font-size: 11px;\n            color: #9ca3af;\n            margin: 4px 8px 0;\n            white-space: nowrap;\n        }\n\n        .message.incoming .message-time {\n            margin-left: 16px;\n        }\n\n        .message.outgoing .message-time {\n            margin-right: 16px;\n        }\n\n        .chat-composer {\n            padding: 20px 24px;\n            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;\n            background: white;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            gap: 12px;\n        }\n\n        .message-input {\n            flex: 1;\n            padding: 12px 16px;\n            border: 1px solid #d1d5db;\n            border-radius: 24px;\n            font-size: 14px;\n            outline: none;\n            transition: border-color 0.2s;\n        }\n\n        .message-input:focus {\n            border-color: #6366f1;\n        }\n\n        .send-button {\n            width: 44px;\n            height: 44px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            background: #6366f1;\n            color: white;\n            font-size: 18px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            transition: background-color 0.2s;\n        }\n\n        .send-button:hover {\n            background: #5856eb;\n        }\n\n        /* Mobile Responsive */\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .conversation-panel {\n                display: none;\n            }\n\n            .back-button {\n                display: block;\n            }\n\n            .chat-panel {\n                width: 100%;\n            }\n\n            .message-bubble {\n                max-width: 80%;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"app-container\">\n        <!-- LEFT PANEL - Conversation List -->\n        <div class=\"conversation-panel\">\n            <div class=\"conversation-header\">\n                <h1 class=\"app-title\">Pulse</h1>\n                <div class=\"search-box\">\n                    <input type=\"text\" class=\"search-input\" placeholder=\"Search conversations...\">\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"conversation-list\">\n                <div class=\"conversation-item active\">\n                    <div class=\"avatar\">SM</div>\n                    <div class=\"conversation-content\">\n                        <div class=\"conversation-top\">\n                            <span class=\"contact-name\">Sarah Miller</span>\n                            <span class=\"conversation-time\">2:34 PM</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"conversation-bottom\">\n                            <span class=\"last-message\">Hey! Are we still on for lunch tomorrow?</span>\n                            <span class=\"unread-badge\">2</span>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"conversation-item\">\n                    <div class=\"avatar\">JD</div>\n                    <div class=\"conversation-content\">\n                        <div class=\"conversation-top\">\n                            <span class=\"contact-name\">John Davis</span>\n                            <span class=\"conversation-time\">1:15 PM</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"conversation-bottom\">\n                            <span class=\"last-message\">Thanks for the project update!</span>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"conversation-item\">\n                    <div class=\"avatar\">EW</div>\n                    <div class=\"conversation-content\">\n                        <div class=\"conversation-top\">\n                            <span class=\"contact-name\">Emily Wilson</span>\n                            <span class=\"conversation-time\">11:42 AM</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"conversation-bottom\">\n                            <span class=\"last-message\">Can you send me the design files?</span>\n                            <span class=\"unread-badge\">1</span>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"conversation-item\">\n                    <div class=\"avatar\">MT</div>\n                    <div class=\"conversation-content\">\n                        <div class=\"conversation-top\">\n                            <span class=\"contact-name\">Mike Thompson</span>\n                            <span class=\"conversation-time\">10:28 AM</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"conversation-bottom\">\n                            <span class=\"last-message\">Perfect! See you at the meeting.</span>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"conversation-item\">\n                    <div class=\"avatar\">LB</div>\n                    <div class=\"conversation-content\">\n                        <div class=\"conversation-top\">\n                            <span class=\"contact-name\">Lisa Brown</span>\n                            <span class=\"conversation-time\">Yesterday</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"conversation-bottom\">\n                            <span class=\"last-message\">The presentation went really well!</span>\n                            <span class=\"unread-badge\">5</span>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"conversation-item\">\n                    <div class=\"avatar\">RJ</div>\n                    <div class=\"conversation-content\">\n                        <div class=\"conversation-top\">\n                            <span class=\"contact-name\">Robert Johnson</span>\n                            <span class=\"conversation-time\">Yesterday</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"conversation-bottom\">\n                            <span class=\"last-message\">Let me know when you're available</span>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"conversation-item\">\n                    <div class=\"avatar\">AS</div>\n                    <div class=\"conversation-content\">\n                        <div class=\"conversation-top\">\n                            <span class=\"contact-name\">Anna Smith</span>\n                            <span class=\"conversation-time\">Monday</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"conversation-bottom\">\n                            <span class=\"last-message\">Great job on the new feature!</span>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- RIGHT PANEL - Chat Thread -->\n        <div class=\"chat-panel\">\n            <div class=\"chat-header\">\n                <button class=\"back-button\">\u2190</button>\n                <div class=\"chat-contact-info\">\n                    <div class=\"chat-avatar\">\n                        SM\n                        <div class=\"online-dot\"></div>\n                    </div>\n                    <span class=\"chat-contact-name\">Sarah Miller</span>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"chat-messages\">\n                <div class=\"message incoming\">\n                    <div class=\"message-bubble\">Hey! How's your day going?</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-time\">1:45 PM</div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"message outgoing\">\n                    <div class=\"message-time\">1:47 PM</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-bubble\">Pretty good! Just finished the morning meetings. How about you?</div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"message incoming\">\n                    <div class=\"message-bubble\">Same here! I wanted to ask about lunch tomorrow</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-time\">2:15 PM</div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"message incoming\">\n                    <div class=\"message-bubble\">Are we still meeting at that new Italian place?</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-time\">2:15 PM</div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"message outgoing\">\n                    <div class=\"message-time\">2:18 PM</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-bubble\">Absolutely! I made a reservation for 12:30 PM</div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"message outgoing\">\n                    <div class=\"message-time\">2:18 PM</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-bubble\">I heard their pasta is amazing \ud83c\udf5d</div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"message incoming\">\n                    <div class=\"message-bubble\">Perfect! I can't wait to try it</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-time\">2:20 PM</div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"message incoming\">\n                    <div class=\"message-bubble\">Should we invite Mike and Emily too?</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-time\">2:21 PM</div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"message outgoing\">\n                    <div class=\"message-time\">2:25 PM</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-bubble\">Great idea! I'll send them a message</div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"message incoming\">\n                    <div class=\"message-bubble\">Awesome! See you tomorrow then \ud83d\ude0a</div>\n                    <div class=\"message-time\">2:34 PM</div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"chat-composer\">\n                <input type=\"text\" class=\"message-input\" placeholder=\"Type a message...\">\n                <button class=\"send-button\">\u2192</button>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>", "rv_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Pulse - Messaging App</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n  